                        </td>
                        <td>This is a controller we've used before to do the function this project needs it to. I am familiar with the 
                            software interface and understand how to set up the controller to read the potentiometers. Additionally, the other
                            members of this group are familiar with this controller as well, which will make debugging significantly easier. 
